{"tid":693572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又加分] 天水圍三女童約網友見面遭非禮　警拘兩男包括一休班警","createTime":"2018-06-07T14:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:14.000Z","uid":23707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"42458a00dd9d92a9233a22fc6189f2a7bdb75967","tid":693572,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"天水圍三女童約網友見面遭非禮　警拘兩男　包括一休班警<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/196956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F196956&d=Pmc%2BG0prstH3r%2FvXcVSltE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fc3ac5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/196956</a>"},{"pid":"68d8f5be2f2e3c8197350dbe4753b763b1574e8f","tid":693572,"uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"天水圍發生風化案，三名女童遭人非禮，兩名涉案男子被捕，當中一人為休班警。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前接報，指一名女童懷疑在天水圍區被非禮。新界北總區重案組人員接手調查案件，其間發現一名28歲姓黃男子及一名32歲姓余休班警分別在網上社交媒體結識三名女童，其後他們各自相約於天水圍區見面，三名女童之中，兩名女童懷疑被黃男非禮；而姓余休班警亦非禮當中兩名女童。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日分別在屯門區及天水圍區以涉嫌非禮拘捕黃男，而姓余休班警，則涉嫌非禮及向年齡在十六歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為而被捕。二人已獲准保釋候查，分別須於6月下旬及７月上旬向警方報到。案件由新界北總區重案組第三隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方指警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> goal!!!!!"},{"pid":"6b5bdd2bc40144b67b1b5d2ecb5cd3953173451e","tid":693572,"uid":108090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"啲警察佢幾皮野一個月 去叫雞算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc644c51564be8c4d801a123ed9d798f618b684","tid":693572,"uid":3857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"休班警+1分"},{"pid":"514bcf21b2273662ca068221fb82e08fb49de32a","tid":693572,"uid":7961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fc644c51564be8c4d801a123ed9d798f618b684","tid":693572,"uid":3857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"休班警+1分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"加2分係咪先岩"},{"pid":"29362761af514505167664b700ed65115aac2833","tid":693572,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5adf7fa5e19944ca52fb99cf4302df6d82b84f82","tid":693572,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}